Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to take care of something very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:14.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like I'm forgetting my own face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagiri Pharmaceuticals, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do they really
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}perform human experiments here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:24.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not Harima Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:28.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spend as much money as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have all the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love you, Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.52,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This world is full of fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:18.91,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They say stuff like "I love you," or "I adore you," and rob others of their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:22.78,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Look only at me. Stay by my side and desire me."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Such spoiled kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My love isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:34.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's more perfect, and has no boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks for the money. {lit deposit}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want me to buy you something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, the vending machine is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still haven't found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell were the guards doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}According to the guard on duty last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seiji had stayed at the same hotel for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but suddenly changed locations in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.95,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He answered his phone around seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If something were to happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:10.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He promised not to leave Ikebukuro, so they'll find him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:11.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:16.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think will happen to us if the cops see that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have the patience for you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.92,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To me, that thing was just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:39.67,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was like one of those pretty, expensive, imported dolls my uncle bought for me as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.95,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never liked dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:51.22,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think he sent them because he wanted to please me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.73,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but because he liked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Seiji, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see what we've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:14.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.48,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The house was always tranquil,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.56,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and Seiji and I were always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.82,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Before Seiji was born, I often spent my time in my uncle's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I even had free access to his study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.64,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That thing was sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:42.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My uncle would stare at that thing, apparently smuggled in from a foreign county, as though it fascinated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.90,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He would even talk to it from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.05,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It truly was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}More beautiful than any doll he ever sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.36,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Without feeling a sliver of cruelty or curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:59.33,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I perceived the head itself as a living entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.59,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was nothing more to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:12.22,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I secretly let my brother into the study to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe I just wanted to share that secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.31,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's when it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:39.03,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the one regret I still have to contend with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the first time we've met, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:57.66,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did the list of illegal immigrants help you, Yagiri Namie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:07.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, I'm so overjoyed and honored that the chief of Yagiri Pharmaceuticals' Sixth Research Lab has personally come to such an unworthy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Find out where my brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care how much it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I haven't gotten hold of him since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He must be somewhere in Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, it hasn't been that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you so worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A girl with scars around her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, he's at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Get your ass moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:47.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't there a lot of other important things I should investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:53.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a rumor that the foreign Nebula Inc. will take over your company, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, you'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.31,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Orihara Izaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, that's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never would have imagined that a woman as successful as you would be in love with her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:11.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Yagiri Namie-san I know is an excellent woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, even though the company's run by your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your father was fired because of his mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I heard the current president, your uncle, is a rather laid-back person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:26.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, you joined the company and didn't let your youth stop you from rising to the position of chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not to mention your beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see you did your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It shouldn't be a problem for you to find my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't think it's a good idea to interfere with his affairs so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one else can protect him but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:50.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, stalkers don't realize what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They think they're protecting—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never group me with stalkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, I'll do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, informants aren't the same as cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What rules are you playing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just one question:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you jealous of that girl with the scar around her neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way I'd be jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:36.61,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This crimson, rusty jealousy burning in my heart is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:40.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sis, there's someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:46.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I realized that Seiji was acting stranger with every passing day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.00,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He would recklessly ask to enter our uncle's study,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.19,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the first thing he'd do after sneaking in was gaze at that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He didn't fall in love with a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.24,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but something without feelings, let alone a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.61,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to get that thing as far away as I could from Seiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:14.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so the moment I joined the company, I asked my uncle to let me use it as a research subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:22.23,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since then, Nebula Inc. started staying in contact with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.97,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and I was desperate to keep our research from leaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was when my security card was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.73,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Only I had that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:44.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:51.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The feeling I had back then was neither fear nor anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.31,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was an indescribable feeling of bliss and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.80,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seiji needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:21.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not talking about the body. I mean that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're the one who took her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave that to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:42.30,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know that a stupid girl named Harima Mika was stalking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.66,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When she let herself into his room and saw that thing, Seiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:52.14,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:57.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like there's no need for you to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cops will take him into custody and call you soon, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, don't worry when I say, "the cops."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not a biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.82,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But we just got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.06,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really glad that you love me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please, take me somewhere far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be alone with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A lover's quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Help! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're not suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let go of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know why, but you need to chase after her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always wanted to say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Go on and leave this to me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, {\i1}you{\i0}  should wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let go dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's my soul mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is she like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:28.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't know anything about the person you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quite irresponsible, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:49.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That doesn't matter when you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then how can you call her your soul mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need no other reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:01.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You cannot put love into words!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll show it through my actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I like you more than Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:26.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I'll let you off the hook for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fuck, it's gonna bleed when I pull it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Should I buy a band-aid first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or should I buy some super glue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your head's attached to a body and walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When you caught her, a high schooler got in your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:06.14,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and when you were chasing her, another high schooler popped up and ran away with your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you honestly expect me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But why was Shizuo-kun there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, I completely forgot to mention that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:21.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was waiting in the park because of the job Izaya gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then Shizuo passed by and we started talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:31.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Well everything's okay, since he called and said the job was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Orihara-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like you're still perplexed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're always welcome to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:50.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And besides! Why the heck is my head on another body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:55.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, as I haven't seen it, I can't say anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if you want to hear my theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He found a girl whose body matched your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and replaced her head with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or maybe it's a fresh corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That... That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.80,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't believe I did anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:30.42,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After that incident, I created her for Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.09,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.40,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She...{************** check}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must have been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But nothing happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:43.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even after she ran away from here and spent time together with Seiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.56,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my love didn't waver at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His love exists because he can use my love as a stepping stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:54.96,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I know that he knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.13,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's quite perverted. {not in the sense of fucking}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.19,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yet, I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.55,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That bastard was wearing Raira Academy's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.22,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway I have to find that kid from Raira Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, I'll have a talk with my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean the head didn't scream until it saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:22.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you want from that "head" that's living as a human, as a whole entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you telling me that you'll sever the head just because you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Selty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.36,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that my head and memories are lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:43.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to admit that everything I've done in the past twenty years was for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll definitely get her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened to your cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:00.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though I put it in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.10,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay. Leave everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.23,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That rascal. {she means the head}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:33.72,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That doll should have done what a doll does: nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.06,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And quit interfering with my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.58,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to regret anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Call all the subcontractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care if it's dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:53.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have no other choice, destroy it on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:22.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like everyone's pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:26.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So fun! So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:30.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are so many things in this city even I, The Informant, don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Things appear and vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's exactly why I can't leave a city where people gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.16,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've got butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:48.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}humans should love me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:56.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have you calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.48,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you answer my questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said you don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:09.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words... Amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... Well, I'll be repeating myself...
